fields.name: comment
fields.value:
Data Distribution

Each slave handles 1 MS file, thus #_of_ms_files ==  #_of_slaves, and iterates the MS file one chunk (of time intervals) at a time

The chunk size (aka tilesz) determines the total number of  Timeslots (NTime) iterations

Each Slave reads in 
tilesz x Nbaseline x Nchan samples per "time" chunk, each sample has 4 complex numbers, i.e. 8 double numbers.
